{"tid":786990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"石籬二邨兩男互斬 一人頸中刀重創","createTime":"2018-08-20T10:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T11:45:44.000Z","uid":122,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"99529985e94f618105451bd72aa76dcf5635b51f","tid":786990,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T10:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180820/large/1534759590_85e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180820%2Flarge%2F1534759590_85e5.jpg&h=a5cde9da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葵涌發生斬人案，下午4時許，兩名男子於石籬二邨石福樓對開因瑣事爭執，兩人大打出手，其間他們均取出利刀襲擊對方，街坊見狀報案。警員接報趕至，現場有一名男子頸及面受傷，大量流血，將其送院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n警員在附近一帶兜截，在街市對開發現一名男子身上染有血迹，懷疑與案有關，將其拘捕。被捕男子事後亦由救護車送往醫院治理。警方正就事件展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/realtime/breaking\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking&d=LaYFzeWo0jmsFzezrbAsBy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=d8e7c47f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking&h=3e5520f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/realtime/breaking</a>"},{"pid":"38009aaabee1cf3e24a9c59310bbab505df035dc","tid":786990,"uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T10:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.gamersky.com/showimage/id_gamersky.shtml?http://img1.gamersky.com/image2017/02/20170221_my_227_7/image001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamersky.com%2Fshowimage%2Fid_gamersky.shtml%3Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2017%2F02%2F20170221_my_227_7%2Fimage001.jpg&h=f55d847a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢老大戰？"},{"pid":"a7869c5346d63bfdef48f63be43f549d80377e0c","tid":786990,"uid":4493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"香港完全退返去80年代<img src=\"/assets/face